profile_positions.description:
Involved in all commercial sales, which are related to back office activities and make arrangements for Sales Executives; 
Searching for new customers in order to generate additional and new business. 
Relationship management and cross-selling with existing customers and key account support.
Format Offers and quotations and perform all other tasks in support of the sales activities;

I am the point of contact for clients and coordinate the necessary follow-up of customer requests or inquiries from customers.
